source.name: Trademark Registration Multi-Page TIFF Images (1870-2008)
source.description: Contains the images of each trademark registration published weekly (Tuesdays) from 1870 to 2008 in Tagged Image File Format (TIFF) Revision 6.0 with CCITT Group 4 Compression (multi-page TIFFs) from the USPTO USAMark product. Approximately 1 TB (compressed).
